@startuml

Inventory - Inventory System
Customer - Customer
Supplier - Supplier

Good - Good
Order - Order
Invoice - Invoice
Receipt - Receipt
Request - Request
Transaction - Transaction

Inventory:
    state AddGood[Add Good]
    state UpdatePrice[Update Price]
    state RemoveGood[Remove Good]
    state ExpiredGoods[Expired Goods]
    state OrderSupplier[Order Supplier]
    state GenerateInvoice[Generate Invoice]
    state SearchItems[Search Items]
    state CalculateDiscountTax[Calculate Discount and Tax]
    state GenerateReceipt[Generate Receipt]
    state ReplaceItemOrCancel[Replace Item or Cancel]
    state RecordRequest[Record Request]
    state ViewTransactions[View Transactions]

Customer:
    state PlaceOrder[Place Order]
    state PayConfirmation[Payment Confirmation]

Supplier:
    state ReceiveOrder[Receive Order]

Inventory - AddGood: [*] --> AddGood
AddGood - UpdatePrice: PlaceOrder --> UpdatePrice
UpdatePrice - RemoveGood: GenerateInvoice --> RemoveGood
RemoveGood - ExpiredGoods: PayConfirmation --> ExpiredGoods
ExpiredGoods - NotifyUser[Notify User]: *
ExpiredGoods - RemoveExpiredGoods: *
RemoveExpiredGoods - RemoveGood: NotifyUser --> RemoveExpiredGoods
OrderSupplier - OrderReceived[Order Received]: ReceiveOrder --> OrderReceived
OrderReceived - GenerateInvoice: *
GenerateInvoice - SearchItems: *
SearchItems - CalculateDiscountTax: *
CalculateDiscountTax - GenerateReceipt: *
GenerateReceipt - PlaceOrder: *
PlaceOrder - PayConfirmation: *
PayConfirmation - ReplaceItemOrCancel: *
ReplaceItemOrCancel - RecordRequest: *
RecordRequest - ViewTransactions: *
ViewTransactions - [*]: ViewTransactions --> [*]

@enduml
